cui_name: Cervical high grade squamous intraepithelial lesion
reasoning: HSIL (CIN 2/3) detection rate from cervical screening programs. Global average ~150 per 100k women screened annually, based on WHO cervical cancer screening data. Corresponds to CIN 2 and CIN 3 combined. Varies significantly by screening coverage and HPV prevalence.
source: WHO/ICO Information Centre on HPV and Cervical Cancer (2005)
